Whew, as expected, dancing like that made me really hot, so...

617
00:47:55,879 --> 00:47:58,549
じゃん！
Ta-da!

618
00:47:58,549 --> 00:48:03,979
羽織を、上着、羽織を脱ぎました！
I took off my haori coat!

